Â  Â  <section class="impact-story" id="impact">

Â  Â  Â  Â  <div class="container">

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <div class="section-title">

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <h2>Impacts on Our World</h2>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <p>How Terra's data helps us understand and address environmental challenges affecting communities worldwide</p>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  </div>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <div class="story-container">

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <div class="story-text">

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <h3>Climate Change & Extreme Weather</h3>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <p>Terra's instruments have documented rising global temperatures, changing precipitation patterns, and increasing frequency of extreme weather events. This data helps communities prepare for and respond to climate-related challenges.</p>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <p>From farmers adjusting planting seasons to coastal communities planning for sea-level rise, Terra's observations provide critical information for adaptation strategies.</p>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <button class="btn" onclick="openModal('climate')">Learn More</button>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  </div>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <div class="story-visual">

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/climate/800/400.jpg" alt="Climate Change Visualization" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;">

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  </div>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  </div>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â Â 

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <div class="story-container" style="margin-top: 60px;">

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <div class="story-visual">

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/airquality/800/400.jpg" alt="Air Quality Visualization" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;">

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  </div>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <div class="story-text">

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <h3>Air Quality & Public Health</h3>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <p>MOPITT and other Terra instruments track pollutants like carbon monoxide, aerosols, and ozone in our atmosphere. This data helps identify pollution sources and assess air quality impacts on public health.</p>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <p>Cities use this information to implement clean air policies, issue health advisories, and reduce exposure to harmful pollutants that affect respiratory health.</p>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <button class="btn" onclick="openModal('air')">Learn More</button>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  </div>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  </div>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â Â 

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <div class="story-container" style="margin-top: 60px;">

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <div class="story-text">

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <h3>Ecosystems & Biodiversity</h3>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <p>Terra monitors changes in forests, wetlands, and other ecosystems, providing crucial data on habitat loss, deforestation, and ecosystem health. This information supports conservation efforts and biodiversity protection.</p>

Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <p>Researchers and policymakers use these observations to identify critical habitats, track restoration efforts, and understand how climate change affects species distribution.</p>

