Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  <p>MODIS has documented shrinking snow cover and ice sheets, while CERES has measured Earth's energy imbalance, showing how our planet is trapping more heat than it radiates to space. ASTER has captured glacial retreat and changes in land surface temperature.</p>

